          \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGoogle Messages is good, but it\u0026#39;s certainly not perfect. Most Android users will end up using it because it offers excellent integration with the rest of Android and other Google services. Of course, Google isn\u0026#39;t one to rest on its laurels, and is \u003ca href=\"http://www.androidpolice.com/google-messages-new-ui-changes/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econstantly making new changes to the app\u003c/a\u003e in order to ensure that the experience continues to get better. \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"2389-4885-9b8a968906d1\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/google-messages-tips-and-tricks/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/googlemessages.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/googlemessages.jpg